items.name: Mikami Reiko - Ghost Sweeper Mikami
items.description:
This LoRA tries to replicate a classic anime character from the 90's: Mikami Reiko.

It was trained on Anything V5 in order to try to get as close to her looks from the old TV Show, I used 24 images with 1488 steps.

Is usually too strong at 1.0 weight so try lower values to allow flexibility, it can work fine at 0.55 weight along with the tags retro style and/or 1990's, but any value under that will make it lose the resemblance to Mikami. adding negative inversions like Unspeakable-Horrors-Composition-4v and verybadimagenegative_v1.3 is highly recommended to achieve better quality generations.

Trigger word should be mikm

Basic prompt example: mikm, purple dress, tube dress, bare shoulders, orange hair, long hair, smile, breasts, cleavage, sitting, green eyes, crossed legs, <lora:MiKmv1-1500bND16:1>

I think this turned out great, please try it out and share your results!

items.description:
随手融合的一个模型，比例已经忘记了，只是把之前炼制的lora融合到新模型里：

所用的底模为 revAnimated 1.2.2

增加对比度使用了 Ally's mix

替换亚洲脸使用了 BRA

烘焙了 clearVae

最后加上自己早期训练的仙侠服装Lora以及水墨风格Lora,

未使用 BWM, 就成了这么一个模型。

可以使用两个触发词：inkwash style (水墨风格) | xianxia style (仙侠风格)。

现在还有点瑕疵，等有空了再调整....自己有基础的，也可以按照上面的逻辑自己融合，比如自己替换其他风格衣服等....

本人郑重声明：

本模型禁止用于训练基于明星、公众人物肖像的风格模型训练，因为这会带来争议，对AI社区的发展造成不良的负面影响。

machine translation:

A model that was fused casually, the proportions have been forgotten, just integrate the previously refined lora into the new model:

The counter used is revAnimated 1.2.2

Increased contrast using Ally's mix

Replaced Asian face with BRA

baked clearVae

Finally, add Xianxia Lora I trained in the early days and the Ink Wash Lora,

Without using BWM, it becomes such a model.

Two trigger words can be used: inkwash style (ink wash style) | xianxia style (Xianxia style).

There are still some flaws, and I will adjust it when I have time... If you have a foundation, you can also integrate it according to the above logic, such as replacing other styles of clothes by yourself

solemnly declare:

This model is prohibited from being used to train style models based on the portraits of celebrities and public figures, because it will bring controversy and have a negative impact on the development of the AI ​​community.

items.name: masamasa Style
items.description:
This model is based on anything4.5 trained from the picture of masamasa , and it is recommended to use weights between 0.6 and 0.8.

There have been many controversies about the training and use of art style models, but they are also a difficult part to avoid in the process of AI painting progress.

Therefore, it is recommended to use such art style models as a kind of existence similar to potions, by matching Loras of different art styles with different weights to form images with different styles (although this may lead to bad results, it is worth trying).Alternatively, it can be used to match your favorite character models. Anyway, I hope not to compare it with the artist's own work and make rude remarks, which will harm the community's environment.

At the same time, there are still many problems to be discovered in this model. In short, hope you have a good time.

items.name: SDArt : Un-Mythical Creatures
items.description:
Model presentation

This is a model related to the "Challenge of the WeekEnd" contest on Stable Diffusion discord.


You can find this dataset in a more complete model, SDArt : Complete Edition.

This present version is trained on dedicated tokens per user, and doesn't work like you may be used to.

I try to make a model out of all the submissions, for people to continue enjoy the theme after the event, and see a little of their designs in other people's creations. The token stays "SDArt" and I balance the learning on the low side, so that it doesn't just replicate creations.

The pictures were tagged using the token "SDArt", and an arbitrary token given to the user that submitted it.

The dataset is available below and is composed of 31 pictures.


This week's theme

[Excerpt from “Chronicles of Curiosity: Professor Lawrence's Field Guide”]

It was a creature of un-mythical origins, imbued by the forest itself. Its body was sleek and agile, with fur the color of a moonless deep blue midnight sky and eyes that glowed like embers in the darkness. But what truly set it apart were the petals that bloomed from its back, opening and closing like a flower that only blossomed at night.

The creature's habitat was the forest floor, where it moved with an effortless grace that defied the laws of physics. Its body seemed to flow like water over the tangled roots and fallen leaves, its every movement a thing of hypnotic beauty. It had a natural affinity for the plants around it, but not in the way that one might expect. Rather than using them for sustenance, the creature communed with them, drawing strength from the very life force that pulsed through their veins.

And so it was that the creature of un-mythical origins, born from the very essence of the earth itself, came to be known by a name whispered on the lips of those who had glimpsed its rare presence - Nightshade.

🐉 Delve into mythology and create a brand new creature that doesn't exist in legends or myths. Give these creatures of non-legend a new lease of life! 🦞

Challenges:

  • At least one feature inspired by a real-life animal or plant.

  • Incorporate an element of the creature's habitat into its design.

  • Give your creature a name.

What's the next entry in the Field Guide?

items.name: Elegant Mermaid Dress
items.description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

To support me you can buy me a coffe at https://ko-fi.com/antonioriolo

Training settings:

40 images, 15 steps, 12 epochs, you find many epochs (with test images using plot xy script) on my Patreon while supporting me.


Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.2-0.6 (0.3 best results in my experiments)

  • Keys: wearing mermaid dress, movie premier gala, standing on the red carpet, wedding dress, back view

  • Adviced Image sIze: 512x768, 512x912

this model isn't hard to use even if it doesn't always give what you expect.

My advice is to use always higher height in the image to show all the dress and use keywords like full body.

You might want a mermaid wedding dress in that case you can just write "wearing mermaid dress, wedding dress"

Also, you might want to pick the dress color, in that case just specify it, the training images have a lot of variety, SD should be able to understand any dress color.

Many of the images i posted have DPM Karras but any DPM++ gives better result usually.

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians

items.name: leg panties (片足パンツLoRA)
items.description:
A LoRA that generates panties that are caught on one leg when they are about to be taken off.

Ver.3 with higher performance was completed because the understanding of LoRA has improved a little.

Compared with Ver.2,

The impact on image quality has been greatly suppressed, and the probability of generating panties has also been improved.

Be sure to use the "panties around one leg" prompt.

Up to Ver.2, the recommended strength was 0.6 to 0.8, but it seems that many models of Ver.3 do not distort the image even with 1.

It works well with 2D and 2.5D illustration models, but it seems that it is not good at live-action models, and the probability drops considerably.

others prompt,

"bottomless"

"skirt lift"

You may add more as needed.

I'm still dissatisfied with the shape of the generated panties, so if my understanding of LoRA improves and I can complete a good LoRA, I'll publish it, but I have no idea when that will be. I do not understand.

(May 8, 2023)

Added Ver.2.0. See "About this version" for details.

(June 2, 2023)

Added Ver.3.0.

///以下翻訳前の原文///

脱ぎかけで片脚にひっかかってるパンツを生成するLoRAです。

LoRAへの理解が少し向上した為に、より性能の高いVer.3が出来上がりました。

Ver.2と比較すると、

画質への影響が大きく抑えられ、またパンツの生成確率も向上しました。

"panties around one leg" promptを必ず使ってください。

Ver.2まではお勧めの強度は0.6～0.8まででしたが、Ver.3は1でも画像が乱れないモデルが多い様です。

2次元、2.5次元イラストのモデルでは上手く動作しますが、実写のモデルは苦手の様で、かなり確率が下がります。

bottomless

特化了俯视的【第一人称】被膝枕视角，可以在低权重下搭配looking_down和负提示的legs来辅助。另外，搭配上一些南半球（underboob）的角色有奇效。只不过这种视角在一部分大模型中显示的俯角不够大，可能是大模型本身数据没涉猎到吧。

LORA of hizamakura and mimikaki. It will work better for some characters with underboob. Checkpoint should be chosen carefully, because some of them may not be able to display the effect.

items.name: Senna | League of Legends
items.description:
Lora trained on Senna from League of Legends

models used

anime: MeinaUnreal, ChinoMix, MeinaMix

2,5D: Discord Mix, Lyriel, fantasticmix_real,

tags: senna \(league of legends\), 1girl, dark-skinned female, dreadlocks, cape

optional: hooded cape, green eyes, glowing eyes

negative embeddings: embedding:bad-hands-5, embedding:ng_deepnegative_v1_75t, embedding:bad-artist, embedding:EasyNegative

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • VAE: orangemix.vae (for 2,5D pictures), vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned (for realistic models), kl-f8-anime2, blessed2.vae (for anime models)

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras or DPM++ 2M Karras

  • Steps: 20 to 35

  • Clipskip: 2

  • Upscaler : img2img in comfyui using 4x-UltraMix_Smooth

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9 (mostly 7 and 8)

  • LORA weight for txt2img: 0.5-1 (0.7-0.8 recommended)

  • Denoise strength for img2img: 0.4 to 0.7

If you want the exact same settings, just drag and drop the picture into ComfyUI

for the pictures i used comfyui

items.name: XSarchitecturalV3Commercialbuildingrendering
items.description:
XSarchitecturalV3Commercialbuildingrendering

使用建议:

如果您想获得参数，请下载图像并使用稳定扩散特性。

任何现代建筑形式

这次作为XS建筑模型的重要更新，我们不仅解决了柔光曝光的问题，而且在建筑形式上进行了更加多样化的尝试。在渲染软件的帮助下，我们还制作了各种材料的立面表达。提示越详细，提示的效果就越好。您可以在提示符中输入“图像左侧的汽车”，它仍然会显示。

配合一些TI, VAE等使用文件

如果你觉得用起来不错，记得给我打个五星评价哦❤❤❤！这对我来说非常重要（特别是带图像）

如果您有任何问题，请通过xsarchitecturalstudio@gmail.com与我联系（商务相同）

Suggestions for use form XS:

If you want to get the parameters, download the image and use the stable diffusion feature.

Any modern architectural form

This time, as an important update of XS architectural model, we not only solved the problem of soft light exposure, but also made more diverse attempts on architectural forms. With the help of rendering software, we also made the facade expression of various materials. The more detailed the prompt is, the better the prompt will perform. You can enter "car on the left side of the image" into the prompt and it will still display.

TI, VAE and other documents for use

If you think it's good, give me a five-star review❤❤❤,This is very important to me (especially with images)

If you have any questions, please contact me at xsarchitecturalstudio@gmail.com (Same for business)

XSからの使用アドバイス:

パラメータを取得したい場合は、画像をダウンロードし、安定拡散機能を使用してください。

現代の建築様式では

今回、xs建築モデルの重要なアップデートとして、ソフトな光の露出の問題を解決しただけでなく、建築形態についてもより多様な試みを行った。また、レンダリングソフトを活用して、様々な素材のファサード表現も行いました。プロンプトが詳細であればあるほど、プロンプトのパフォーマンスは向上します。プロンプトに「画像の左側にある車」と入力しても表示されます。

TI、VAEなどのファイルを一緒で使ってください

モデルをいいと思ったら5つ星をつけて返事してお願い❤❤❤！（特にイメージを持ったら）

何かご質問がございましたら、xsarchitecturalstudio@gmail.comにメールしてください。(ビジネスも同じです)
